text: Yemelyanov at the 2016 Summer Olympics. Alexandr Yemelyanov (born January 1, 1984) is a Kazakhstani sprint canoeist. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the Canoeing at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Men's K-4 1000 metres race as part of the tenth-place Kazakhstan team. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani male canoeists Category:Olympic canoeists of Kazakhstan Category:Canoeists at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Asian Games gold medalists for Kazakhstan Category:Asian Games silver medalists for Kazakhstan Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for Kazakhstan Category:Asian Games medalists in canoeing Category:Canoeists at the 2002 Asian Games Category:Canoeists at the 2006 Asian Games Category:Canoeists at the 2010 Asian Games Category:Canoeists at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 2006 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 2010 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 2014 Asian Games
